@startuml
actor Browser
participant App as "Shiny App / Starlette"
participant OAuthHandler
participant "OAuth Provider" as OAuthProvider
participant SessionManager
participant "ISC Client" as ISCClient

Browser -> App: GET /login
activate App
App -> OAuthHandler: generate_authorization_url()
activate OAuthHandler
OAuthHandler -> OAuthProvider: GET /authorize?client_id=...&redirect_uri=...&scope=...&state=...
OAuthHandler --> App: auth_url, state
deactivate OAuthHandler
App -> Browser: 302 Redirect to auth_url\nSet-Cookie: oauth_state=<state>
deactivate App

Browser -> OAuthProvider: GET /authorize?...&state=...
activate OAuthProvider
OAuthProvider --> Browser: 302 Redirect to /callback?code=...&state=...
deactivate OAuthProvider

Browser -> App: GET /callback?code=...&state=...
activate App
App -> Browser: read cookie oauth_state
App -> OAuthHandler: validate_state(state)
activate OAuthHandler
OAuthHandler --> App: valid/invalid
deactivate OAuthHandler
alt state valid
    App -> OAuthHandler: exchange_code(code)
    activate OAuthHandler
    OAuthHandler -> OAuthProvider: POST /token\n(code, client_secret, redirect_uri)
    OAuthProvider --> OAuthHandler: access_token, refresh_token, expires_in
    OAuthHandler --> App: TokenSet
    deactivate OAuthHandler

    App -> SessionManager: create_session(token_set)
    SessionManager --> App: session_id
    App -> Browser: 302 Redirect /\nSet-Cookie: session_id=<session_id>\nDelete-Cookie: oauth_state
else invalid state
    App -> Browser: 302 Redirect /?error=invalid_state
end
deactivate App

=== Subsequent requests ===

Browser -> App: GET /
activate App
App -> SessionManager: get_session(session_id cookie)
SessionManager --> App: Session(token_set,user_info)
App -> ISCClient: get_client_for_session(session, oauth_handler)
activate ISCClient
alt token not expired
    ISCClient --> App: cached client
else token expired
    ISCClient -> OAuthHandler: refresh_token(refresh_token)
    activate OAuthHandler
    OAuthHandler -> OAuthProvider: POST /token\n(refresh_token, client_secret)
    OAuthProvider --> OAuthHandler: new access_token
    OAuthHandler --> ISCClient: new TokenSet
    deactivate OAuthHandler
    ISCClient --> App: refreshed client
end
deactivate ISCClient
App --> Browser: render app

=== Logout ===

Browser -> App: POST /logout
activate App
App -> SessionManager: delete_session(session_id)
App -> ISCClient: evict_client(session_id)
App --> Browser: {"success": true}\nDelete-Cookie: session_id
deactivate App
@enduml
